00:18:51,345 --> 00:18:53,336
- Sandwiches, ma'am?
- No.

240
00:18:53,514 --> 00:18:55,004
No, thank you.

241
00:18:56,017 --> 00:18:58,542
I certainly had an interesting day.

242
00:18:58,719 --> 00:19:03,588
I went riding. In the afternoon,
I took a walk around the property

243
00:19:03,758 --> 00:19:06,784
