had sent her many messages.

246
00:19:26,214 --> 00:19:29,206
You have 35 new messages.

247
00:19:29,383 --> 00:19:33,444
It's Sam Jones. call me.
I can't stop thinking about you.

248
00:19:36,057 --> 00:19:40,221
